name: Web v2022.11.0
body:
- Updated login flow that splits username and master password into separate pages
- New passwordless login option that allows users to login with an already-authenticated device
- Organization administration tabs have been restructured, such as the new Billing and Reporting tabs, to provide easier discovery for common administrative tasks 
- SCIM-triggered events will log from SCIM instead of Unknown
- SCIM API key will be obfuscated by default
- Improved web vault load times and performance for accounts with thousands of vault items

Thank you! :blue_heart:

A big shout-out to the following community members for their `2022.11.0` release contributions!

[Sammy Chang](https://github.com/schang1146)

- Add DuckDuckGo’s email forwarding service

[David Frankel](https://github.com/frankeld)
- Display creation date in vault item history

name: Desktop v2022.9.0
body:
- Added Fastmail to forwarded email alias providers
- Accessibility fix: remove appBlurClick which in some circumstances led to unwanted loss of focus ( Community PR, thank you [Patrick H. Lauke](https://github.com/patrickhlauke)!)
- Accessibility fix: ARIA/structure fixes (Community PR, thank you [Patrick H. Lauke](https://github.com/patrickhlauke)!)
- Accessibility: Improvement of item edit for URIs and custom fields (Community PR, thank you [Patrick H. Lauke](https://github.com/patrickhlauke)!)
- Bug fix for failure to render vaults when switching accounts on Linux
- Bug fix for rate limiting UI errors
- Bug fix for inability to update user master password after Owner does an Admin Password Reset
- Bug fix for wrong repository redirection when checking for Updates (Community PR, thank you [Matthis Radke](https://github.com/proton-byte)!)

name: Browser v2022.9.0
body:
- Added Fastmail to forwarded email alias providers
- Self-hosting customers can now pre-configure environment URLs for browser extensions, streamlining rollout for end users
- Accessibility: remove `appBlurClick` which in some circumstances led to unwanted loss of focus( Community PR, thank you [Patrick H. Lauke](https://github.com/patrickhlauke)!)
- Bug fix for safari attachment downloads
- Bug fix for inability to update user master password after Owner does an Admin Password Reset

name: Web v2022.9.0
body:
- Created new flow for combined account/organization creation to simplify trial registration 
- Added Fastmail to forwarded email alias providers
- Improvements to organization menu styles
- Improvements to disabled organization display
- The main Provider Portal screen now has at-a-glance seat and plan reporting for each client organization
- Organizations will now have an event recorded in the event log when an owner or admin performs a vault export
- Bug fix for “manage all collections” custom permissions
- Bug fix for account referenceData not being populated
- Bug fix for incorrect “learn more” url for Premium
- Bug fix for small typo in twoStepLogin modal (Community PR, thank you [Patrick H. Lauke](https://github.com/patrickhlauke)!)
